      <li><strong>FAQ / myth-bust posts.</strong> &quot;Most people think Invisalign costs $8,000. Here&apos;s what it actually costs.&quot;</li>
      <li><strong>Behind-the-scenes posts.</strong> Real team, real workspace, real process. Customers love human details.</li>
