      <li><strong>Event posts.</strong> Workshops, open houses, free consultations, holiday hours. Event posts last through the event date — longer than standard 7-day posts.</li>
      <li><strong>Media-mention posts.</strong> Press coverage, awards, third-party endorsements. Authority signals.</li>
      <li><strong>Lead-generation posts.</strong> Free consultations, downloadable guides, newsletter signups. Pair with a clear CTA button.</li>
